{"tid":1021490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"App Store下載排行榜第一名  打敗抖音的熱門App","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T09:45:14.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"edf884ea12ef734d31fee26bae666c7444fd39e7","tid":1021490,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"彭博資訊報導，專門推廣習近平政治思想的APP「學習強國」上線僅一個多月，在蘋果應用程式商店（App Store）中國國內下載排行榜已衝上第一名，打敗熱門通訊軟體微信，以及短片社群應用程式「抖音」。<br />\n<br />\n「學習強國」App的內容包含有關習近平的新聞、影音片段，甚至展示「習近平思想」。習近平思想在2017年中共十九大後被寫入了黨章。這款App在今年1月1日上線，由中共中央宣傳部推出，它的下載量激增凸顯中共在加強控制中國之際，努力要讓年輕一代的中國民眾接觸「黨思想」。<br />\n<br />\n隨著中國全大會下月將登場，中共近期推出宣傳，鼓勵學習習近平學說。學習強國App本身會依照使用者登入的次數、貼文或發問給予積分，並且支援微信式的互傳訊息通訊。根據中國財經網報導，黨員被鼓勵使用這款App。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/02/14/realtime/5923735.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F02%2F14%2Frealtime%2F5923735.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600%26exp%3D3600&h=4fab5b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3644128#prettyPhoto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3644128%23prettyPhoto&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=46377372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3644128#prettyPhoto</a>"},{"pid":"8464207d59b15b896f8ca68cb72f2427c94de23c","tid":1021490,"uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"瘋狂下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c41e7bad2769107f3b4c65d24aa9e31d9080859","tid":1021490,"uid":63877,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:39:30.000Z","